{"tid":264240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽到屋企人沖澡打飛機 可以點","createTime":"2017-05-30T15:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T10:14:22.000Z","uid":101367,"like":1,"dislike":143,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28ca4de312db17b79f3ab426dc9af1d266c5729e","tid":264240,"uid":101367,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:53:20.000Z","msg":"我間房同廁所好近 只要開咗門就會聽到廁所水聲<br />\n加上屋企係用浴缸 全家都有浸浴沖涼<br />\n早幾個禮拜開始 聽到哥哥係廁所有啲啪啪啪聲 似拍打水面 唔止一兩下 都有十幾秒特別大聲 加淋身嘅聲 所以我就覺得哥哥係浴缸打飛機<br />\n試過閂房門都聽到聲 聽到呢啲聲好唔舒服 我唔知係咪佢唔知咁應聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係話唔俾佢打飛機 但可唔可以唔好咁明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到呢幾日好似聽到爸爸係廁所都有啪啪聲 定其實係我諗多咗<br />\n真心覺得好老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我到底可以點"},{"pid":"a6fbe8f5de73699ae6bfbe1ae0d42f4c7b00c942","tid":264240,"uid":5883,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:53:57.000Z","msg":"太長 唔睇"},{"pid":"3ef88abd66caf29054ba3eca956b71b9aaa19951","tid":264240,"uid":72177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:55:04.000Z","msg":"點樣可打J打到啪啪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4e5a241bdb8506c9c601185652f4279062eb15","tid":264240,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"2個互含互射囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c42f85cd5c02543baa9bc9245dcb83db210c1ae","tid":264240,"uid":20448,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:55:47.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 而家打飛機都關你事啊<br />\n我係你細佬實用碌撚發你塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb384a4662537656b88711faad5db5958455ebd","tid":264240,"uid":52287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣可打J打到啪啪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/l